{"tid":1183487,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"奇洛李維斯與甜筒 好人好事一則","createTime":"2019-06-03T03:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T03:58:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2d5704c0487d04144e46916a78fc26d2ff70bdf","tid":1183487,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:03:33.000Z","msg":"James Dator在貼文中寫到：「我在16歲的時候曾在悉尼一家戲院打過工。那時候奇洛李維斯已經憑著《廿二世紀殺人網絡》而走紅。我記得那天是一個星期三的早上，幾乎都沒有人要來看戲。」<br />\n<br />\n「我在售票處發呆，悶得發慌，突然間有一個穿著皮夾克、 牛仔褲和馬術帽的人出現在我面前，我花了30秒才認出面前的人正是奇洛李維斯。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「他想要買一張Johnny Depp主演《From Hell》的票，我當時完全是處於震驚的狀態，然後我做了一個16歲害羞男生會做的事&mdash;&mdash;提出要給他打員工折扣。這樣他就能在單子上簽名，而我就能拿到他的親筆簽名了。」<br />\n<br />\n「但奇洛困惑地拒絕了他的提議：『可是我不在這裡工作呀。』我只好無奈地打消念頭，目送他離開後懊悔地想著：『剛才應該直接問他要簽名的！』」<br />\n<br />\n「過了大概兩分鐘左右，有人敲了敲售票室背後的門，我想當然以為是我的經理。門一打開，是奇洛。」<br />\n<br />\n「我這才知道他買了一個自己根本不吃的甜筒，就是為了給我這個不敢跟他要簽名的傻瓜找一張紙來簽名。」<br />\n<br />\n「他說：『我想你可能是想要我的簽名，所以我簽了這個。』他遞給我一張便利店的發票，背面是他的簽名。然後他轉身離開，把一支甜筒隨手丟進垃圾桶，然後看電影去了。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8kZr43t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8kZr43t.jpg&h=0ab793c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iykbwJx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiykbwJx.jpg&h=3bb0c87f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nxgBHQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnxgBHQk.jpg&h=45244abd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KxmRwJL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKxmRwJL.jpg&h=0cfc1ef4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NtOgHQt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNtOgHQt.jpg&h=5e97268a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZOvZFCd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZOvZFCd.jpg&h=4b03a690&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eosUuvD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeosUuvD.jpg&h=10704001&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"945812be61c15a2520b5b294be844e2763af774d","tid":1183487,"uid":25969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"把一支甜筒隨手丟進垃圾桶"},{"pid":"3834eeb761b6440695e4015a696b6fe9f19df3dd","tid":1183487,"uid":41343,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"945812be61c15a2520b5b294be844e2763af774d","tid":1183487,"uid":25969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"把一支甜筒隨手丟進垃圾桶"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:08:46.000Z","msg":"甜筒是無辜的"},{"pid":"c5418032c169532233adfdcd13db6f086b285414","tid":1183487,"uid":60057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:24:56.000Z","msg":"請埋個男仔食甜筒呀嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"174cdf308493f406c68b17fd8f319fdf368db61d","tid":1183487,"uid":239205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"945812be61c15a2520b5b294be844e2763af774d","tid":1183487,"uid":25969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"把一支甜筒隨手丟進垃圾桶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:26:09.000Z","msg":"環保撚抵制奇洛浪費食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbc83e7688036321b91f7dfec5b232e7b56532f","tid":1183487,"uid":28202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"174cdf308493f406c68b17fd8f319fdf368db61d","tid":1183487,"uid":239205,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"945812be61c15a2520b5b294be844e2763af774d","tid":1183487,"uid":25969,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:07:52.000Z","msg":"把一支甜筒隨手丟進垃圾桶"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:26:09.000Z","msg":"環保撚抵制奇洛浪費食物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T03:57:20.000Z","msg":"唔係環